ZH: 佛教教义中，普度众生是重要的教导。
EN: In Buddhist doctrine, benefiting all sentient beings is an important teaching.

ZH: 佛菩萨的使命就是普度众生。
EN: The mission of Bodhisattvas is to benefit all sentient beings.

ZH: 他一生致力于普度众生。
EN: He devoted his entire life to benefiting all sentient beings.

ZH: 每位信徒都应该有普度众生的心态。
EN: Every believer should have the mindset of benefiting all sentient beings.

ZH: 我们要慈悲地普度众生。
EN: We should compassionately benefit all sentient beings.

ZH: 普度众生是一件充满慈爱的行为。
EN: Benefiting all sentient beings is an act full of love.

ZH: 他的行为体现了他对普度众生的承诺。
EN: His actions reflect his commitment to benefiting all sentient beings.

ZH: 佛弟子们的目标是普度众生。
EN: The goal of Buddhist disciples is to benefit all sentient beings.

ZH: 通过修行，我们可以普度众生。
EN: Through practice, we can benefit all sentient beings.

ZH: 我们要以普度众生为己任。
EN: We should take benefiting all sentient beings as our own responsibility.

ZH: 普度众生的行为会带来善果。
EN: Benefiting all sentient beings' actions will bring about good results.

ZH: 普度众生让我们感到更有价值。
EN: Benefiting all sentient beings makes us feel more valuable.

ZH: 普度众生需要付出很多奉献。
EN: Benefiting all sentient beings requires a lot of dedication.

ZH: 他因为普度众生而受到大家的尊重。
EN: He is respected by all for benefiting all sentient beings.

ZH: 普度众生是我们的共同目标。
EN: Benefiting all sentient beings is our common goal.

ZH: 普度众生不分贵贱，一视同仁。
EN: Benefiting all sentient beings without discrimination, treating them equally.

ZH: 普度众生需要先有一颗善良的心。
EN: Benefiting all sentient beings requires first having a kind heart.

ZH: 他每日普度众生，从不言倦。
EN: He benefits all sentient beings daily, never getting tired of it.

ZH: 通过普度众生，我们也受益匪浅。
EN: Through benefiting all sentient beings, we also benefit greatly.

ZH: 愿一切众生都能受到我们的普度。
EN: May all sentient beings benefit from our efforts.
